---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="My Journey">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h1>My Journey</h1>
      <p>Why I started, where I am now, and where I'm going.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="journey-content prose">
      <section class="journey-section">
        <h2>Why I Started</h2>
        <p>
          I used to play different sports every day of the week. It was a huge part of who I was.
          But after more than a decade of inactivity, chronic lack of sleep, stress, and constant travel,
          my body started breaking down in ways I couldn't ignore anymore.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm now dealing with high glucose levels, shortness of breath, and a general decline in
          overall health. I've tried measuring my glucose and eating healthier, but I'm not seeing
          much improvement from those changes alone.
        </p>
        <p>
          This is my effort to build myself back up from the ground up — a little more systematically
          this time — so that I can fix my broken body and get my health back.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="journey-section">
        <h2>Where I Am Now</h2>
        <p>
          Starting point. I'm at the very beginning of this journey. My current challenges:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>High glucose levels</li>
          <li>Shortness of breath</li>
          <li>General decline in overall health and fitness</li>
          <li>Over a decade of inactivity</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          I've started monitoring my glucose and adjusting my diet, but it's clear that
          nutrition alone isn't enough. I need a comprehensive, systematic approach.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="journey-section">
        <h2>My Goals</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Bring glucose levels back to a healthy range</li>
          <li>Restore cardiovascular fitness — no more shortness of breath</li>
          <li>Rebuild strength and mobility after a decade of inactivity</li>
          <li>Establish sustainable daily habits for long-term health</li>
          <li>Get back to playing sports again</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="journey-section">
        <h2>My Approach</h2>
        <p>
          Build from the ground up, systematically. Rather than trying to do everything at once,
          I'm taking a structured approach:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Measure</strong> — Track glucose, activity, sleep, and how I feel</li>
          <li><strong>Move</strong> — Start with daily walks and basic movement, then gradually increase</li>
          <li><strong>Eat</strong> — Continue improving nutrition with a focus on glucose management</li>
          <li><strong>Sleep</strong> — Prioritize consistent, quality sleep</li>
          <li><strong>Document</strong> — Write it all down so I can see what works and stay accountable</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .journey-content {
    max-width: 750px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .journey-section {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }

  .journey-section h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }
</style>
